<html>

<head>
    <title>Function.prototype.call()</title>
</head>

<body>
    <h1>在一个子构造函数中，可以调用父构造函数的call方法来实现集成</h1>
    <div>
        <span>
            function Animal(species) { this.species = species; alert(this.species); } function Rabbit(name) { this.name = name; Animal.call(this,
            "rabbit"); } var tutu = new Rabbit("bunny"); //alert "rabbit"
        </span>
    </div>
    <script>
        function Animal(species) {
            this.species = species;
            alert(this.species);
        }

        function Rabbit(name) {
            this.name = name;
            Animal.call(this, "rabbit");
        }

        var tutu = new Rabbit("bunny"); //alert "rabbit"
    </script>
</body>

</html>
